Package: spicov
Type: Package
Title: High-dimensional Spiked Covariance Matrix Estimation
Version: 0.1
Date: 2014-06-11
Author: Didier Chételat
Maintainer: Didier Chételat <dc623@cornell.edu>
Description: Computes a high-dimensional spiked covariance matrix estimate 
	by correcting the eigenvalues of a sample covariance matrix. The spiked 
	rank can be specified, or selected automatically (default). See Ch\'etelat 
	and Wells (2014) (arxiv.org/abs/1408.6440).
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.1), RcppArmadillo (>= 0.4.200.0)
Depends: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Suggests: MASS
License: GPL-2
URL: http://www.stat.cornell.edu/~chetelat
Encoding: UTF-8
Packaged: 2014-09-02 00:08:51 UTC; didier
